#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kolorlines; is a simple but highly addictive, one player game for &kde;. "
#| "&kolorlines; has been inspired by well known game of <application>Color "
#| "Lines</application>, written for <application>DOS</application>, by Olga "
#| "Demina, Igor Ivkin and Gennady Denisov back in 1992."
msgid ""
"&kolorlines; is a simple but highly addictive, one player game by &kde;. "
"&kolorlines; has been inspired by well known game of <application>Color "
"Lines</application>, written for <application>DOS</application>, by Olga "
"Demina, Igor Ivkin and Gennady Denisov back in 1992."
msgstr ""
"O &kolorlines; é un xogo simples mais altamente adictivo para un único "
"xogador para o KDE. O &kolorlines; foi inspirado nun xogo coñecido - o "
"<application>Color lines</application>, escrito para o <application>DOS</"
"application> por Olga Demina, Igor Ivkin e Gennady Denisov en 1992."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The goal of &kolorlines; is quite plain. The player has to move the "
#| "colored balls around the game board, gathering them into the lines of the "
#| "same color by five. Once the line is complete it is removed from the "
#| "board, therefore freeing precious space. In the same time the new balls "
#| "keep arriving by three after each move, filling up the game board."
msgid ""
"The goal of &kolorlines; is quite plain. The player has to move the colored "
"marbles around the game board, gathering them into the lines of the same "
"color by five. Once the line is complete it is removed from the board, "
"therefore freeing precious space. In the same time the new marbles keep "
"arriving by three after each move, filling up the game board."
msgstr ""
"O obxectivo de &kolorlines; é bastante simple. O xogador ten de mover as "
"bólas coloradas pola área de xogo, recolléndoas das liñas da mesma cor en "
"grupos de cinco. Cando a liña está completa retírase da área de xogo, "
"liberando así un espazo necesario. Ao mesmo tempo, as bólas novas continúan "
"a chegar en grupos de tres despois de cada xogada, enchendo a área de xogo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kolorlines; cannot be won, and is played against the high score "
#| "exclusively. The game ends once the whole game board is filled up with "
#| "balls."
msgid ""
"&kolorlines; cannot be won, and is played exclusively to get a high score. "
"The game ends once the whole game board is filled up with marbles."
msgstr ""
"&kolorlines; non pode vencerse, e xógase exclusivamente contra a táboa de "
"mellores puntuacións. O xogo termina cando o taboleiro do xogo estiver "
"enchido de bólas."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Como xogar"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Obxectivo:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Move the colored balls around the game board, gathering them into the "
#| "lines of the same color by five."
msgid ""
"Move the colored marbles around the game board, gathering them into the "
"lines of the same color by five."
msgstr ""
"Mover as bólas coloradas pola área de xogo, recolléndoas nas liñas da mesma "
"cor en grupos de cinco."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When &kolorlines; starts you are presented with the game board split into "
#| "81 squares (the game board is 9x9 squares), and right away three new "
#| "colored balls appear on the board. Use your mouse to move the balls from "
#| "cell to cell to group them into the lines of the same color. However, "
#| "after each of your moves the computer drops three more marbles onto the "
#| "board. To avoid filling up the board you should gather the balls into "
#| "lines of 5 or more balls. When such a line is complete, the balls are "
#| "removed from the field and your score grows."
msgid ""
"When &kolorlines; starts you are presented with the game board split into 81 "
"squares (the game board is 9x9 squares), and right away three new colored "
"marbles appear on the board. Use your mouse to move the marbles from cell to "
"cell to group them into the lines of the same color. However, after each of "
"your moves the computer drops three more marbles onto the board. To avoid "
"filling up the board you should gather the marbles into lines of 5 or more "
"marbles. When such a line is complete, the marbles are removed from the "
"field and your score grows."
msgstr ""
"Ao iniciar &kolorlines; aparece a área de xogo dividida en 81 cadrados (a "
"área corresponde a cadrados 9x9) e logo aparecen tres bólas coloradas novas. "
"Usa o rato para mover as bólas dunha cela para outra, agrupándoas en liñas "
"da mesma cor. Con todo, despois de cada unha das xogadas, o computador larga "
"tres bólas máis en xogo. Para evitar que se encha a área de xogo hai que "
"reunir as bólas en liñas de 5 ou máis bólas. Cando unha destas liñas quedar "
"completa, as bólas son retiradas do xogo e ti gañas puntos."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74 index.docbook:76 index.docbook:93 index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note:"
msgstr "Nota:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The new balls will not be added to the field after a line removal. "
#| "Instead you will be rewarded with yet another move before a new triplet "
#| "of balls is added."
msgid ""
"The new marbles will not be added to the field after a line removal. Instead "
"you will be rewarded with yet another move before a new triplet of marbles "
"is added."
msgstr ""
"As bólas novas non se engaden ao campo despois da retirada dunha liña. En "
"vez diso, recompénsaseche con máis outra xogada antes de engadirse un "
"conxunto triplo de bólas novas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The increase in score depends solely on the amount of the erased balls."
msgid ""
"The increase in score depends solely on the amount of the erased marbles."
msgstr ""
"O aumento na puntuación depende unicamente na cantidade de bólas borradas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76 index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are playing with <guimenuitem>Show Next</guimenuitem> feature enabled "
"the increase in score is less than if <guimenuitem>Show Next</guimenuitem> "
"feature is disabled."
msgstr ""
"Se estiveres a xogar coa funcionalidade <guimenuitem>Amosar o seguinte</"
"guimenuitem> activa, o aumento na puntuación é menor que con esta "
"funcionalidade desactivada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kolorlines; cannot be won, and is played against the high score "
#| "exclusively. The game ends once the whole game board becomes filled up "
#| "with balls."
msgid ""
"&kolorlines; cannot be won, and is played exclusively to get a high score. "
"The game ends once the whole game board becomes filled up with marbles."
msgstr ""
"&kolorlines; non pode vencerse, e xógase exclusivamente contra a táboa de "
"mellores puntuacións. O xogo termina cando o taboleiro do xogo estiver "
"enchido de bólas."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Regras do xogo, estratexias e suxestións"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules"
msgstr "Regras do xogo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "After each player’s move the game will add three more balls to the board."
msgid ""
"After each player’s move the game will add three more marbles to the board."
msgstr ""
"Despois de cada quenda do xogador o xogo engade tres bólas máis á área de "
"xogo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To free up the space on the board player has to group the balls of the "
#| "same color into an uninterrupted horizontal, vertical, or diagonal line "
#| "by five or more."
msgid ""
"To free up the space on the board player has to group the marbles of the "
"same color into an uninterrupted horizontal, vertical, or diagonal line by "
"five or more."
msgstr ""
"Para liberar o espazo en xogo hai que agrupar as bólas da mesma cor nunha "
"liña ininterrompida na horizontal, vertical ou na diagonal con cinco ou máis "
"elementos."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To initiate the move simply click on the source ball to select it, then "
#| "click on the destination square to complete the move."
msgid ""
"To initiate the move, simply click on the source marble to select it, then "
"click on the destination square to complete the move."
msgstr ""
"Para iniciar o movemento, basta premer a bóla de orixe para seleccionala, e "
"despois o cadrado de destino para terminar a xogada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "A ball can only be moved into the squares that are vacant and not "
#| "occupied by any other ball."
msgid ""
"A marble can only be moved into the squares that are vacant and not occupied "
"by any other marble."
msgstr ""
"Unha bóla só pode moverse para os cadrados que estean libres e non estean "
"reservados por outra bóla."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "In the same time the square in question must be freely accessible."
msgid "In the same way, the square in question must be freely accessible."
msgstr ""
"Ao mesmo tempo, o cadrado en cuestión deberá estar accesíbel de forma libre."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The square is freely accessible when there are no other balls blocking "
#| "the path to it."
msgid ""
"The square is freely accessible when there are no other marbles blocking the "
"path to it."
msgstr ""
"O cadrado está accesíbel cando non existiren bólas que bloqueen a ruta ata "
"el."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The path is considered blocked if any part of it is currently being "
#| "occupied by a ball."
msgid ""
"The path is considered blocked if any part of it is currently being occupied "
"by a marble."
msgstr ""
"A ruta considérase bloqueada se calquera parte da mesma for ocupada nese "
"momento por unha bóla."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In &kolorlines; the path is automatically calculated by the game. If "
#| "there is no possible (open) route to the destination cell, a friendly "
#| "notification will be displayed."
msgid ""
"In &kolorlines;, the path is automatically calculated by the game. If there "
"is no possible (open) route to the destination cell, a friendly notification "
"will be displayed."
msgstr ""
"En &kolorlines;, o traxecto calcúlao automaticamente o xogo. Se non existir "
"ningunha ruta posíbel (aberta) ata á cela de destino, aparece unha "
"notificación amigábel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In order to successfully transfer a ball to a desired cell where the path "
#| "is blocked to, player has to clear the path first."
msgid ""
"In order to successfully transfer a marble to a desired cell where the path "
"is blocked to, player has to clear the path first."
msgstr ""
"Para conseguir transferir unha bóla para unha cela desexada, na cal a ruta "
"estea bloqueada, o xogador ten de limpar antes a ruta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To clear the path the player simply has to move all the blocking balls "
#| "out of the way, therefore freeing the route."
msgid ""
"To clear the path the player simply has to move all the blocking marbles out "
"of the way, therefore freeing the route."
msgstr ""
"Para limpar o traxecto, o xogador simplemente ten de mover todas as bólas "
"que o bloqueen para fóra do camiño, liberando deste modo a ruta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The scores are awarded for each line of balls removed off the game board."
msgid ""
"The scores are awarded for each line of marbles removed off the game board."
msgstr "Adquírense puntos por cada liña de bólas retirada da área de xogo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Estratexias e suxestións"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keep a close look on the bar showing the next three marbles to be dropped "
"onto the field (unless <guimenuitem>Show Next</guimenuitem> feature is "
"disabled). More often then not you will appreciate the information if "
"provides."
msgstr ""
"Convén manter a atención na barra que mostra as tres bólas seguintes que van "
"entrar no campo (a menos que a funcionalidade <guimenuitem>Amosar o "
"seguinte</guimenuitem> estea desactivada). A maior parte das veces a "
"información que fornece será moi apreciada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Try to keep at least a half of the game board cleared. Letting the balls "
#| "to pile up will almost certainly lead to a loss."
msgid ""
"Try to keep at least a half of the game board cleared. Letting the marbles "
"to pile up will almost certainly lead to a loss."
msgstr ""
"Intenta manter polo menos metade da área de xogo limpa. Se deixares as bólas "
"amorearse, case de certeza que iso acabará en derrota."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To make your game easier always keep more than one line of the same balls "
#| "ready for clearing. This can be achieved by building the consecutive "
#| "lines of the same balls everywhere possible, instead of concentrating on "
#| "one line at a time."
msgid ""
"To make your game easier, always keep more than one line of the same marbles "
"ready for remove. This can be achieved by building the consecutive lines of "
"the same marbles everywhere possible, instead of concentrating on one line "
"at a time."
msgstr ""
"Para facilitar o xogo, intenta manter sempre máis dunha liña das mesmas "
"bólas libre para limpar. Isto pode conseguirse se construíres as liñas "
"consecutivas das mesmas bólas onde for posíbel, en vez de te concentrares "
"nunha liña de cada vez."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Try to keep more than three almost completed lines existing on the game "
#| "board at all times. Almost completed means that they are four same balls "
#| "in length, and only one ball remains until their completion."
msgid ""
"Try to keep more than three almost completed lines existing on the game "
"board at all times. Almost completed means that they are four same marbles "
"in length, and only one marble remains until their completion."
msgstr ""
"Intenta manter máis de tres liñas case completas na área de xogo en todo "
"momento. Case completas significa que existen catro e que só falta unha para "
"terminalas."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "Exemplo:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you have an almost completed line and the pathway to it suddenly "
#| "becomes blocked with another ball, don’t just move that ball. Try to find "
#| "a sequence of the balls of the same kind that you can continue with the "
#| "moved ball. If such sequence exists and is accessible – then move the "
#| "blocking ball there."
msgid ""
"If you have an almost completed line and the pathway to it suddenly becomes "
"blocked with another marble, don’t just move that marble. Try to find a "
"sequence of the marbles of the same kind that you can continue with the "
"moved marble. If such sequence exists and is accessible – then move the "
"blocking marble there."
msgstr ""
"Se tiveres unha liña case completa e o traxecto ata ela quedar de repente "
"bloqueado por outra bóla, non movas unicamente esa bóla. Intenta atopar unha "
"secuencia coas bólas do mesmo tipo para que poidas continuar a mover a bóla. "
"Se esta secuencia existir e estiver accesíbel, daquela move para aí a bóla "
"que bloquea."

